 Reference Number: 250 1004 MHU Job Description: Our client is a junior mining company with operations in Central Africa. The main duties are to develop and execute strategies to optimize and manage Cost of Sales through an annual sourcing plan managed by the Source to Contract/Category Management section, productivity optimization with ordering of goods/services by the Procurement section, effective Warehousing and Inventory control, exporting from DRC and in-bound logistics by the Materials Management section, clearing of all inbound products and the clearing and logistics of all finished products in/out of the DRC by the Logistics & Clearing section, whilst ensuring service delivery to all internal customers in the DRC by the Site Supply Chain Managers and supported departments by ensuring delivery of goods and services to the Company. Responsibilities: Requirements: Qualification and Skill Benefits and Contractual information: